<template><div><h1 id="剑指-offer-05-替换空格" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#剑指-offer-05-替换空格" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 剑指 Offer 05. 替换空格</h1>
<p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/ti-huan-kong-ge-lcof/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/ti-huan-kong-ge-lcof/<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<h2 id="问题描述" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#问题描述" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 问题描述</h2>
